Package: diffTop
Date: 08-01-2021
Title: Differential topic analysis using latent Dirichlet allocation
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pratheepa", "Jeganathan", email="jpratheepa31@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Susan", "Holmes", role = c("aut","ctb")))
Maintainer: Pratheepa Jeganathan <jpratheepa31@gmail.com>
Description: Compute the median Bayesian posterior of topic proportions in each sample, multiply the proportions by the library size and round to an integer, and use this as the abundance of the topics in each sample to test differentially abundant topics.
